-- Qatar Asks Potsdam Institute to Study Global Warming Impact
-- B y   R e e d   L a n d b e r g
-- 2012-12-05T06:44:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-05/qatar-asks-potsdam-institute-to-study-global-warming-impact.html
Qatar entered into a partnership with
the Potsdam Institute for Climate Impact Research to study the
effects of global warming on the nation, a spokesman for the
country said at a briefing.  Sheikha Mozah Bint Nasser a Al-Missned, who is chairperson
of the Qatar Foundation charity, signed an agreement outlining
the work in Doha today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Reed Landberg in Doha at 
 landberg@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alessandro Vitelli at 
 avitelli1@bloomberg.net  